Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,1:23:34.52,scritta MD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,0)\alpha&H90&\pos(1808.286,181)}MY DRAMA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:01:44.06,Crediti,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,1500)}traduzione ed encoding by www.mydrama.altervista.org
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A beautiful place full of smiles♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Where imaginations about you grow wildly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪The winter sun is like your white teeth♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Expecting your visit all day long♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Like the light breeze\Nand the fragrance of flowers in May and June♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Hesitate to embrace you and my words stumble♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Time passes hurriedly,\Nleaving a photo of us and sunflowers♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Too flimsy to be scrutinized♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Welcome to my world and explore its beauty♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I can offer you my clumsy gentleness♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Welcome to my lonely island, too♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Only fish and migratory birds have been here♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Maybe I'm too clumsy and evasive♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Tired of troubles,\Nall I want is to hide you secretly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hidden Love]\N[Adapted from the novel Hidden Love by Zhu Yi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Episode 12]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll settle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with this framework.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll quickly address
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the issue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of upgrading the visuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also update
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the program schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell other colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've talked to the building security department
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,strengthening the security here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If Jiang Ying comes again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll notify you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this troubling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't she let go of you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was fortunate this time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that she didn't see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your relative's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what she would have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dwell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on living
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get back to work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Until what time did you study last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Don't come]\NIt was almost 2 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your revision
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the technical overview?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(After this,)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,(don't come directly to my office)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,(or my house.)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know in advance before coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you lend me your notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to catch up on this subject too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[La-la la-la la-la]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this question so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't solve it, let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I must solve it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to eat something first
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to replenish my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(Is he not planning)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,(to call and explain it to me?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on this path below,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be better if you try and test it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to slack off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,(But it was fortunate this time)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that she didn't see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,your relative's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what she would have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Brother No. 2]\N(When's your exam?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,(Have you bought your plane ticket home\Nfor the holidays?)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sang Zhi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,(Next week.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,(I bought a ticket for the 19th.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,(Okay.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Flight for the 19th]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Brother No. 2]\N(When will you be free after the exams?)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,(Let's have a meal together.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sang Zhi]\N(Maybe I won't have time.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,(She might go out with her friends.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(Forget it.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(Okay.)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't focus at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail the exam this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be all his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Weak Chen]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you fight with Chen Qiang?\N(*Qiang means strong and capable.)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he capable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only capable when trying to annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he's extremely weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak Chen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[10 January, Wednesday]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's imperative for me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to change my mood immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wei,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done enduring the bitterness of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Only drinking can relieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After the exam is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your mom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will call you in a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,can we go after the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to text Jiang Ming
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to officially notify everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that Weak Chen is not to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the person for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,(Baby, answer the phone...)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be down there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wei,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant Chen Qiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,have something on your mind lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I could feel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been feeling down these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it started
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from the day you delivered\Nthe electronic peephole camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the relative you sent
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the electronic peephole camera to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,happen to be your crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,something did happen that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not considered
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm overthinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys still keep in touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you treat him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,really nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't treat you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you should move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He treats me well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Chapter 12: Courage. If I could]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Five.\N-Be more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonstrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one are you drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ruin my rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going home tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free tomorrow.\NSo I can send you to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have training tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to send me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go for your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your drink nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This one has a stronger kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I drink it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I get drunk quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Try a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't usually drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling dizzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean five, five, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to try adding
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that screen space ambient occlusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That will make the entire environment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,more three-dimensional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I think of that?\NI'll go and try adding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Duan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Duan Jiaxu]\N(You're going back tomorrow.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,(Have you packed your luggage?)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's going to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,(I'll send you to the airport.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for taking some of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to dedicate a song
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay!\N-Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♪How do I describe your face?♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Cute with a hint of shyness♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I really want to have♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A little bit of something with you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Can I call you this?♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Standing like a fool downstairs at your place♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Dialing the phone♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Looking at the cooling egg tart♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Ming to be good at singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Ming looks handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:14:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he's not as handsome as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Since the day I met you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've fallen in love with you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪They're all about you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Watching the ebb and flow\Nof the ocean's surface♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪It reminds me of you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Carefully♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I store you in my mind♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A repeating melody♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you reply to my messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of the bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Qinghong Music
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,2002 Music Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait inside for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To catch a drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't let me go and see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you want to come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we not worry if you go back like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you drink a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is coming to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk her out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay, go.\N-Go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drink that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for my brother to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not wearing thick enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really not cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang Zhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dedicate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that song to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to stay like this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bench there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you walk over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel even worse like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiaxu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drink a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Sang Zhi's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I go to the same university as Sang Zhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Jiang Ming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says you can drink at a bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a grown-up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I visit a bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you can't drink this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I be there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that when I grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are still
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,many things I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe I just dare not do them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like throwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to throw up, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel better after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,sit over there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're squatting in the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel even worse if you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry you there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel nauseated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel like throwing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When have I ever been mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hold on a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too windy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry you on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you've just had surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do any heavy lifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you carry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up and I'll carry you on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I wipe off the dust because you're still there♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I weigh over 45 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I hide my wish under a band of stars\Nlike a clumsy kid♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I weigh over 45 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is my chest is still flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I weigh over 45 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:23:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Every inch of the wound is softly veiled\Nwithin the halo's radiance♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.05,0:24:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Every night freezes into an eternal day\Namidst the fireworks♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be too sad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.66,0:24:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.70,0:24:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.94,0:24:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you must not be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.18,0:24:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You unlocked the hidden corners of my heart♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,can I carry you home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.66,0:24:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I can no longer hide all those sweet thoughts♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.94,0:24:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.58,0:24:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Growing up with you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.46,0:24:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'm just afraid♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.62,0:24:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.18,0:25:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Losing the fairy tales you promised♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.34,0:25:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.53,0:25:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪In the flowing universe♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.26,0:25:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Our meetings secretly filling the gaps\Nin the Milky Way♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.58,0:25:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.38,0:25:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what if
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.94,0:25:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to throw up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.82,0:25:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you throw up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.10,0:25:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,give me a heads-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.26,0:25:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try not to sway too much
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.74,0:25:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll feel more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.34,0:25:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.86,0:25:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.34,0:25:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't feel like throwing up doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.92,0:25:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiaxu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.98,0:26:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.78,0:26:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've been hiding in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.82,0:26:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.18,0:26:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.86,0:26:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.78,0:26:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.90,0:26:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.82,0:26:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he just doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.10,0:26:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.46,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.14,0:26:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.43,0:26:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.26,0:27:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.94,0:27:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.34,0:27:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.06,0:27:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of the person you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.50,0:27:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.38,0:27:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.74,0:27:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of person he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.38,0:27:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he treat you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.38,0:27:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me that much, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.30,0:27:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.22,0:27:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.86,0:27:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.38,0:28:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't how to put it into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.38,0:28:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.46,0:28:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.78,0:28:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also really nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.62,0:28:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's nice to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just nice to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like a central air conditioning system.\N(*Being nice to many of the opposite gender)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.38,0:28:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So he made you so heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.94,0:28:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's someone like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.46,0:28:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,stop liking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.14,0:28:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.02,0:29:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang Zhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.06,0:30:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the kind of guy you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.10,0:30:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I become like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.34,0:30:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll only be good to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.66,0:30:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, our Sang Zhi
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.62,0:30:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.46,0:30:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,be so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.14,0:30:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting someone else take care of you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.50,0:30:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't put me at ease at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.86,0:30:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just keep quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.94,0:30:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.90,0:31:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My situation has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.38,0:31:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've paid all my debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.58,0:31:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty great personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.94,0:31:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.54,0:31:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a bit older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was 21,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.82,0:31:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you thought I was old.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.02,0:31:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, rounding it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.54,0:31:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you're almost twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.74,0:31:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang Zhi is a grown-up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.54,0:32:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.14,0:32:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,(I threw up.)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.02,0:32:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(I threw up on Jiaxu.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.58,0:33:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,said...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.78,0:33:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.98,0:33:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What was there to say
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.86,0:33:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to a drunkard like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.78,0:33:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Brother No. 2]\N(Are you awake?)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.06,0:33:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,(I asked your roommate)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.74,0:33:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,(to wake you up at nine.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.66,0:33:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(All the flights at this time)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.74,0:33:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(are sold out.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.74,0:33:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(You can't change your flight.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.94,0:33:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,(So you have to get up.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.30,0:33:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,(Or else you won't be able to go back.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.34,0:33:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(After you wake up, drink more water.)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:33:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(I'll pick you up at ten)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.50,0:33:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(and take you to the airport.)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.90,0:34:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.74,0:34:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally awake, Sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.62,0:34:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.46,0:34:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.62,0:34:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Slowly.\N-Watch your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.50,0:34:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the person who sent you back last night
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.50,0:34:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your brother's friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.02,0:34:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your crush whom you mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.38,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,before?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.02,0:34:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.66,0:34:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪My heart jingles when I think of you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.62,0:34:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he was handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but you didn't say he was that handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.34,0:34:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.58,0:34:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.62,0:34:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he's such good-looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to Chen Qiang,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.30,0:34:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chen Qiang is truly weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.58,0:34:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.66,0:34:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.78,0:34:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When he
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.02,0:34:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,sent me back here yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.86,0:34:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,did
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.58,0:34:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.50,0:35:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,look upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.78,0:35:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.70,0:35:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he look upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.54,0:35:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.26,0:35:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.06,0:35:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked pretty fine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.30,0:35:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.70,0:35:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.14,0:35:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.30,0:35:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.70,0:35:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.62,0:35:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.50,0:35:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing? I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.10,0:35:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.58,0:35:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.74,0:35:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,have to watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.98,0:35:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I must never drink anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.54,0:35:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ever drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.38,0:35:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.10,0:35:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kiss him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I did not. I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.14,0:35:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.90,0:35:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.66,0:35:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have confessed your feelings to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.82,0:35:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.26,0:35:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you confess to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.98,0:35:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did confess,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.42,0:35:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.09,0:35:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't wake up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.22,0:35:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then what did you do?\N-What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.10,0:35:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tell us.\N-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.66,0:35:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.54,0:35:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't have vomited, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.14,0:35:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.86,0:35:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you throw up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.94,0:35:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.42,0:35:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,throw up on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.58,0:35:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.10,0:35:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to pack my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.82,0:35:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have to pack up my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.90,0:35:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.26,0:35:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,she did throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.46,0:36:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She threw up on her crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.62,0:36:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.42,0:36:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,threw up on your crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.94,0:36:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he insist on taking me to the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.94,0:36:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I face him
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.34,0:36:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,after what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.26,0:36:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Jiaxu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.46,0:37:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.54,0:37:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.90,0:37:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang Zhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.62,0:37:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Ming.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.54,0:37:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.34,0:37:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.10,0:37:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You had too much to drink last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.58,0:37:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.18,0:37:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.02,0:37:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were drunk last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.98,0:37:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.54,0:37:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if you still remember
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.46,0:37:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.78,0:37:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.10,0:37:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.98,0:37:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.06,0:37:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.10,0:37:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.74,0:37:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sang Zhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.90,0:37:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know your brother was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.26,0:37:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.58,0:37:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.58,0:37:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.30,0:37:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.58,0:37:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't come that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.74,0:38:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.02,0:38:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I sang a song at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.70,0:38:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.94,0:38:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.90,0:38:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was playing the guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.02,0:38:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,as I sang at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.06,0:38:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you even played the guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.86,0:38:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.34,0:38:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared the performance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.94,0:38:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.70,0:38:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.74,0:38:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that song for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.74,0:38:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.22,0:38:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sang Zhi,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.86,0:38:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.66,0:38:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.98,0:38:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be appreciated by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.42,0:38:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can thank him for appreciating you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.62,0:38:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then politely reject him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.22,0:39:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for liking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.26,0:39:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.50,0:39:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.78,0:39:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm into someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.22,0:39:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.22,0:39:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.54,0:39:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.54,0:39:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.90,0:39:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still friends
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.66,0:39:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,after this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.18,0:39:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.98,0:39:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the breakfast with you and eat it on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.18,0:39:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.10,0:39:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.54,0:39:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.58,0:39:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.02,0:39:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.38,0:39:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.10,0:40:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.94,0:40:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then eat more.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.02,0:40:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.50,0:40:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the bar yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.90,0:40:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because we...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We had planned to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.74,0:40:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The exam was difficult, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The bar was also nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.06,0:40:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the campus. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.06,0:40:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mostly students at the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.18,0:40:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so it was not dangerous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.62,0:40:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.30,0:40:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't usually drink much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.18,0:41:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.38,0:41:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My roommates.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.74,0:41:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Roommates?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.82,0:41:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.26,0:41:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,who came out with you yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.42,0:41:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,1.95 meters tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who just gave you a hamburger,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.86,0:41:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is he also your roommate?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.26,0:41:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.94,0:41:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of my roommate's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.18,0:41:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.42,0:41:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.94,0:41:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.26,0:41:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.46,0:42:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.34,0:42:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The breakfast he gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.66,0:42:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a beef burger?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.50,0:42:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.02,0:42:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Jiaxu.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw up on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.54,0:42:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.18,0:42:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't dreaming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.30,0:42:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.54,0:42:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.10,0:42:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.18,0:42:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,give me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.22,0:42:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the clothes I dirtied?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.10,0:43:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give them back to you after I clean them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.94,0:43:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You drank quite a lot last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.98,0:43:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.34,0:43:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you drank too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.34,0:43:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not feeling well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.06,0:43:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So have some fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.30,0:43:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you something hot to drink
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.18,0:43:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when we get to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.26,0:43:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.26,0:43:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.22,0:43:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪My universe is hidden somewhere♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.74,0:43:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪No one can figure out with the glass in between♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.10,0:43:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Which planet♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.70,0:43:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Your name is engraved on♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.70,0:43:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'm like a balloon\Nthat is quietly getting lighter♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.46,0:44:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪My worries are running away from my mind♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.38,0:44:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Silently floating around you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.10,0:44:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,♪As I get closer to you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.90,0:44:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A lime-scented breeze blows♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.30,0:44:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪My fingertips♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.98,0:44:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Pass by your cuffs♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.38,0:44:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Completing a secret love tour♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.50,0:44:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Could I look at you one more time?♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.42,0:44:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Let my heartbeat have one more second♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.26,0:44:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪It's so strange that my gaze♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.48,0:44:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Always follows you around♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.58,0:44:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Could I think of you one more time?♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.98,0:44:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Feeling the unstoppable excitement♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.66,0:44:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Like the first snow waiting for a clear sky♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.10,0:45:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've been waiting for your appearance♪
